'''牛生长激素'''（{{lang-en|bovine somatotropin}}或{{lang|en|bovine growth hormone}}，缩写{{lang|en|bST}}、{{lang|en|BST}}或{{lang|en|BGH}}）是牛[[脑垂体|脑垂体]]分泌的一种[[肽类激素|肽类激素]]，用于调节代谢过程、促进动物生长。研究发现将BST注入母牛体内可以增加其产奶量。<ref name="Brennand">{{cite web |url=https://extension.usu.edu/files/publications/factsheet/FN-250_6.pdf |title=Bovine Somatotropin in Milk |accessdate=2011-03-06 |author=Charlotte P. Brennand, PhD, Extension Food Safety Specialist |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001434/https://extension.usu.edu/files/publications/factsheet/FN-250_6.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

自1970年代[[基因泰克|基因泰克]]发现了控制合成BST的基因后<ref name=Schneider>Keith Schneider. 10 June 1990. [http://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/10/magazine/betting-the-farm-on-biotech.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm "Betting the Farm on Biotech."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1990/06/10/magazine/betting-the-farm-on-biotech.html?pagewanted=all&src=pm |date=20130923020428 }}. ''the New York Times''</ref>，使用[[重组DNA|重组DNA]]技术人工合成'''重组牛生长激素'''（{{lang-en|recombinant bovine somatotropin}}或{{lang|en|recombinant bovine growth hormone}}，缩写{{lang|en|rBST}}或{{lang|en|rBGH}}）成为了可能。此后，[[孟山都|孟山都]]、[[美国氰氨公司|美国氰氨公司]]、[[礼来公司|礼来公司]]、[[普强公司|普强公司]]等大型企业相继开发开发出了商用rBST并提交[[美国食品与药品管理局|美国食品与药品管理局]]审核。<ref>Bijman, J. (1996), "Recombinant Bovine Somatotropin in Europe and the USA." Biotechnology and Development Monitor, No. 27, p. 2-5.[http://www.biotech-monitor.nl/2702.htm] {{Wayback|url=http://www.biotech-monitor.nl/2702.htm |date=20020926093647 }}</ref><ref name=WHO>Bovine Somatotropin. Joint FAO/WHO Expert Committee on Food Additives Monograph [ftp://ftp.fao.org/es/esn/jecfa/vetdrug/41-5-bovine_somatotropin.pdf] {{Wayback|url=ftp://ftp.fao.org/es/esn/jecfa/vetdrug/41-5-bovine_somatotropin.pdf |date=20170518211121 }}</ref>孟山都是其中最早获得批准的公司。除美国外，[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[巴西|巴西]]、[[印度|印度]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]等数十个国家也都批准了rBST的商用。<ref name=Dobs>William D. Dobson. June 1996 [http://www.aae.wisc.edu/pubs/sps/pdf/stpap397.pdf The BST Case] {{Wayback|url=http://www.aae.wisc.edu/pubs/sps/pdf/stpap397.pdf |date=20200921122744 }}. University of Wisconsin-Madison Agricultural and Applied Economics Staff Paper Series No.397</ref>

不过，[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]、[[新西兰|新西兰]]、[[日本|日本]]、[[以色列|以色列]]、[[欧盟|欧盟]]、[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]等国家地区则禁止了市场上的rBST。

美国食品与药品管理局<ref name="fda.gov">{{cite web | url = http://www.fda.gov/AnimalVeterinary/SafetyHealth/ProductSafetyInformation/ucm130321.htm | title = Report on the Food and Drug Administration's Review of the Safety of Recombinant Bovine Somatotropin | accessdate = 2009-05-02 | year = 1999 | archive-date = 2016-08-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160823191323/http://www.fda.gov/AnimalVeterinary/SafetyHealth/ProductSafetyInformation/ucm130321.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]<ref name=WHO/>、[[国立卫生研究院_(美国)|国立卫生研究院]]<ref name="NIH RBST">{{cite book |chapterurl=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK15180/ |chapter=Bovine Somatotropin |title=NIH State of the Science Statements |publisher=National Institutes of Health |access-date=2015-01-19 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130001701/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK15180/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>等机构聲稱使用rBST的奶产品及肉类对人类是安全的。不过在美国，由于部分公众的疑虑，一些生产厂家会在牛奶上贴上“不含rBST”的标签。<ref name="seattlepi.nwsource.com">{{cite news
